data.title: 以至少 50 个字回答问题
data.content: "Describe a challenge that you have experienced. How did you deal with it? Include specific details in your answer."
data.answer: Early in my life, I felt invincible. Rightfully so, I think we all do when we’re young. But one horrible day, I received a phone call that one of my family members had passed away. This is the type of phone call none of us wish to get. It occurred with a family member who I felt was young. Not much older than me. We dealt with the situation at hand. But afterward, it made me really put into perspective how I was living my life. Today, I choose to live life to the fullest, every day. That means enjoying my work, and the people around me, trying to create the best environment and contributing to society.
